episodes.title: Cults and The ETO & capturing the Panama Canal sequence
episodes.description: Hosts Dr. Maggie Aderin-Pocock and Jason Concepcion [..] call on the expertise of Dr. Alexandra Stein, social psychologist and author specializing in cults and extremist groups, to scrutinize the ETO, and explain the real world markers of a cult. SPOILER ALERT: We will be covering episodes 4 and 5 of the series, so if you haven’t watched that far yet, be sure to catch up on Netflix now. The 3 Body Podcast is produced by Netflix and Sony Music Entertainment.
